  "name": "Create Eldritch Cannon",
  "type": "feat",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You must have a token on the scene to use this spell (Warpgate mutation limitation).</p><p>You must have an actor called \"CPR - Eldritch Cannon\" in your actors directory. This can be found in the CPR Actors compendium. You can enable the \"Keep Summon Actors Updated\" setting to have this happen automatically.</p><p>After casting this spell a new feature called \"Eldritch Cannon - Command\" will be available in your features.</p><p>If you use \"Tidy 5e Sheet\" it will automatically be favorited.</p><p>If you use \"Custom Character Sheet Sections\" it will be in it's own section called \"Class Features.\"</p><p>This feature will prompt to use spell slots if you are out of uses.</p><p>You can customize the avatar and token for this feature with custom file paths with the Medkit -&gt; Configure.</p><p>This feature is safe to be renamed.</p>",
